#BUS TICKET MACHINE 

This is simple bus ticket machine which provide tickets to passenger.

#🛠Features
▫️Shows proper destination from ___ to ___

▫️ Differnciate male and female ticket amount.

▫️Shows passengers Age.

▫️Print Amount for single passenger.

#📌Functional Flow
▫️Enter Destination

▫️Enter Gender

▫️Enter Age

#🔍USES
▫️Make work eaiser of the conductor.

▫️Security enhance (proof)

▫️Stores the Data.
